Ticket Number: 00427202
Ticket Subject: Webserver Offline
Ticket Details: Hi,

I am about to implement Endpoint Protector . I had meeting with Claudia
Kurbjuhn we have updated the server everything worked fine. This week I wanted
to download the client package to add it to our software deployment, but for
some reasen the Web server is Offline. I have rebooted the Appliance two times
but still the Webserver is offline and I cannot connect to webinterface. I can
ping the server I can establish a TCP connection to port 22 but port 80 and
443 is closed.

Please assist.

I cannot provide the IDs and Versions due to the fact the webservice is down
and I cannot look it up.

Regards
Benedikt Schallert

Thank you!

Alin Anca
